<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Planting a Tree</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Oct 12, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
God of Hope,
</p>

 <p>
I plant this tree in faith, <br></br>
trusting in your gracious care.
</p>

 <p>
If such a slender trunk <br></br>
can weather the Oklahoma wind, <br></br>
then surely we too can weather <br></br>
these storms of our own making.
</p>

 <p>
May our roots reach down <br></br>
into your sustaining love, <br></br>
our branches reach out <br></br>
to shelter those in need, <br></br>
then reach up to the heavens <br></br>
to bid your Kingdom come, <br></br>
and your will be done.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>







